{
  "id": "S2R00120",
  "title": {
    "product_var": "ZPRODTSK",
    "text": "SPF/PC COMMAND - `=`",
    "version_var": "ZSHRTVER",
    "prefix": "HELP"
  },
  "type": "menu",
  "body": {
    "rows": [
      {
        "type": "command",
        "variable": "ZCMD"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "Purpose"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "Use this command to move directly to any SPF/PC panel. Issue this"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "command from any SPF/PC panel."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "Format"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "=x[.x]"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "Remarks"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "After you become familiar with SPF/PC features and panels, you will"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "find it faster to bypass the menu system and use this short-hand way"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "of identifying the panel you want to work with.  The parameters for"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "this command are simply the primary and secondary (if it applies)"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "option numbers for the panel you want to move to."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "Example"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "=0.2"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "This command would move you to panel 0.2, the PRINTER SETUP panel."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "field_row",
        "fields": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "content": "(Hit"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "content": "ENTER+to return to previous menu)"
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
